Description:
TfGM wishes to appoint and enter into contract for the following work:-
•	Storage of pool bikes and accessories owned by TfGM;
•	Maintenance and repair of pool bikes;
•	Delivery and collection of pool bikes and accessories to and from locations within Greater Manchester; and
•	Associated reporting and record keeping.
The period of service is for 12 months from April 2016 to end of March 2017. TfGM may extend the contract for 12 month periods up to a further 3 years.
